NAME
	preprocessor

DESCRIPTION
	The LPC driver understands the following preprocessor
	directives:

	#include, #define, #if, #ifdef, #ifndef, #else, #elsif,
	#endif, #undef
		same as in ANSI C

	#echo
		the rest of the line is printed to the error output
		(stderr), thus can be caputered into a log file

	#pragma
		see the separate man page

SEE ALSO
	pragma(LPC), predefined(D)
